the lemon-butter mixture. Place a slice of lemon on each filet for added zest.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bake for 10 minutes and serve immediately.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<div id=\"attachment_94224\" style=\"width: 531px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-94224\" data-attachment-id=\"94224\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2020-04-29/baked-lemon-butter-tilapia/img_1225/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?fit=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"IMG_1225\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?fit=888%2C666&amp;ssl=1\" class=\" wp-image-94224\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225-1024x768.jpg?resize=521%2C391\" alt=\"\" width=\"521\" height=\"391\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?resize=1024%2C768&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?resize=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1 250w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?resize=768%2C576&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?resize=1536%2C1152&amp;ssl=1 1536w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?resize=1832%2C1374&amp;ssl=1 1832w, https://i0.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/IMG_1225.jpg?resize=1376%2C1032&amp;ssl=1 1376